<p style="text-indent:43px"><span style=";font-family:仿宋;font-size:21px"><span style="font-family:仿宋">根据教育厅《江西省</span><span style="font-family:仿宋">2024年普通高校专升本考试招生实施方案》和《</span></span><span style=";font-family:仿宋;font-size:21px">江西软件职业技术大学</span><span style=";font-family:仿宋;font-size:21px">2024年退役大学生士兵专升本免试招生</span><span style=";font-family:仿宋;font-size:21px">章程</span><span style=";font-family:仿宋;font-size:21px">》文件精神，经江西省教育考试院第一轮投档结束后，我校各专业均有缺额，现予公布，公开征集志愿。</span></p><p style="text-indent:43px"><strong><span style="font-family:仿宋;font-size:21px">一、</span><span style=";font-family:仿宋;font-size:21px">征集报名时间及方式</span></strong></p><p style="text-indent:43px"><span style=";font-family:仿宋;font-size:21px">凡</span><span style=";font-family:仿宋;font-size:21px">符合免试申请条件</span><span style=";font-family:仿宋;font-size:21px">且未被</span><span style=";font-family:仿宋;font-size:21px">任何高校</span><span style=";font-family:仿宋;font-size:21px">录取的退役大学生士兵，均可登录</span><span style=";font-family:仿宋;font-size:21px">江西软件职业技术大学官网</span><span style=";font-family:仿宋;font-size:21px"><span style="font-family:仿宋">（</span><span style="font-family:仿宋">https://</span></span><span style=";font-family:仿宋;font-size:21px">www</span><span style=";font-family:仿宋;font-size:21px">.</span><span style=";font-family:仿宋;font-size:21px">jxuspt.com</span><span style=";font-family:仿宋;font-size:21px">/）报名参加我校退役大学生士兵免试专升本综合评价。</span></p><p style="text-indent:43px"><span style=";font-family:仿宋;font-size:21px">报名时间为</span><span style=";font-family:仿宋;font-size:21px">2024年3月26日</span><span style=";font-family:仿宋;font-size:21px">9</span><span style=";font-family:仿宋;font-size:21px">:00-3月2</span><span style=";font-family:仿宋;font-size:21px">7</span><span style=";font-family:仿宋;font-size:21px">日</span><span style=";font-family:仿宋;font-size:21px">18</span><span style=";font-family:仿宋;font-size:21px">:00，逾期不予受理。</span></p><p style="text-indent:43px"><strong><span style=";font-family:仿宋;font-size:21px">二、征集专业及计划数</span></strong></p><p style="text-indent:43px"><strong><span style="font-family: 仿宋;font-size: 21px"><img src="http://localhost:20829/upload/img/20240326/1711432426233021793.png" title="1711432426233021793.png" alt="279a8103a24292dc99b0ef192b5535b.png"/></span></strong></p><p style="text-indent:43px"><strong><span style="font-family: 仿宋;font-size: 21px">三、考查时间及办法</span></strong></p><p style="text-indent:43px"><span style=";font-family:仿宋;font-size:21px">综合评价考查采取线下面试的形式，将全程录像并保存备查，学校纪检监察部门对面试全过</span><span style=";font-family:仿宋;font-size:21px">程进行监督。</span></p><p style="text-indent:43px"><span style="font-family: 仿宋;color: rgb(51, 51, 51);letter-spacing: 0;font-size: 21px;background: rgb(255, 255, 255)"><span style="font-family:仿宋">（一）</span></span><span style="font-family: 仿宋;color: rgb(51, 51, 51);letter-spacing: 0;font-size: 21px;background: rgb(255, 255, 255)"><span style="font-family:仿宋">考查</span></span><span style="font-family: 仿宋;color: rgb(51, 51, 51);letter-spacing: 0;font-size: 21px;background: rgb(255, 255, 255)"><span style="font-family:仿宋">面试</span></span><span style="font-family: 仿宋;color: rgb(51, 51, 51);letter-spacing: 0;font-size: 21px;background: rgb(255, 255, 255)"><span style="font-family:仿宋">时间</span></span></p><p style="text-indent:43px"><span style=";font-family:仿宋;font-size:21px">20</span><span style=";font-family:仿宋;font-size:21px">24</span><span style=";font-family:仿宋;font-size:21px">年</span><span style=";font-family:仿宋;font-size:21px">3</span><span style=";font-family:仿宋;font-size:21px">月</span><span style=";font-family:仿宋;font-size:21px">28</span><span style=";font-family:仿宋;font-size:21px"><span style="font-family:仿宋">日</span><span style="font-family:仿宋">1</span></span><span style=";font-family:仿宋;font-size:21px">4</span><span style=";font-family:仿宋;font-size:21px">:</span><span style=";font-family:仿宋;font-size:21px">0</span><span style=";font-family:仿宋;font-size:21px">0</span></p><p style="text-indent:43px"><span style="font-family: 仿宋;color: rgb(51, 51, 51);letter-spacing: 0;font-size: 21px;background: rgb(255, 255, 255)"><span style="font-family:仿宋">（二）携带材料</span></span></p><p style="text-indent:43px"><span style="font-family: 仿宋;color: rgb(51, 51, 51);letter-spacing: 0;font-size: 21px;background: rgb(255, 255, 255)"><span style="font-family:仿宋">1.本人身份证原件、复印件1份；</span></span></p><p style="text-indent:43px"><span style="font-family: 仿宋;color: rgb(51, 51, 51);letter-spacing: 0;font-size: 21px;background: rgb(255, 255, 255)"><span style="font-family:仿宋">2.退伍证原件、复印件1份；</span></span></p><p style="text-indent:43px"><span style="font-family: 仿宋;color: rgb(51, 51, 51);letter-spacing: 0;font-size: 21px;background: rgb(255, 255, 255)"><span style="font-family:仿宋">3.大学期间成绩原件、复印件；</span></span></p><p style="text-indent:43px"><span style="font-family: 仿宋;color: rgb(51, 51, 51);letter-spacing: 0;font-size: 21px;background: rgb(255, 255, 255)"><span style="font-family:仿宋">4.</span></span><span style="font-family: 仿宋;color: rgb(51, 51, 51);letter-spacing: 0;font-size: 21px;background: rgb(255, 255, 255)"><span style="font-family:仿宋">《</span></span><span style="font-family: 仿宋;color: rgb(51, 51, 51);letter-spacing: 0;font-size: 21px;background: rgb(255, 255, 255)"><span style="font-family:仿宋">江西软件职业技术大学</span></span><span style="font-family: 仿宋;color: rgb(51, 51, 51);letter-spacing: 0;font-size: 21px;background: rgb(255, 255, 255)"><span style="font-family:仿宋">202</span></span><span style="font-family: 仿宋;color: rgb(51, 51, 51);letter-spacing: 0;font-size: 21px;background: rgb(255, 255, 255)"><span style="font-family:仿宋">4</span></span><span style="font-family: 仿宋;color: rgb(51, 51, 51);letter-spacing: 0;font-size: 21px;background: rgb(255, 255, 255)"><span style="font-family:仿宋">年退役大学生士兵专升本免试申请表》（附件</span><span style="font-family:仿宋">1）</span></span><span style="font-family: 仿宋;color: rgb(51, 51, 51);letter-spacing: 0;font-size: 21px;background: rgb(255, 255, 255)"><span style="font-family:仿宋">。</span></span></p><p style="text-indent:43px"><span style=";font-family:仿宋;font-size:21px">（三）面试地点</span></p><p style="text-indent:43px"><span style=";font-family:仿宋;font-size:21px">江西软件职业技术大学退役军人教育学院</span></p><p style="text-indent:43px"><span style=";font-family:仿宋;font-size:21px">（四）面试方案</span></p><p style="text-indent:43px"><span style=";font-family:仿宋;font-size:21px">1.</span><span style=";font-family:仿宋;font-size:21px">选聘专家。</span><span style=";font-family:仿宋;font-size:21px">按专业大类分组，每组</span><span style=";font-family:仿宋;font-size:21px">由</span><span style=";font-family:仿宋;font-size:21px">3</span><span style=";font-family:仿宋;font-size:21px"><span style="font-family:仿宋">位专家组成，其中</span><span style="font-family:仿宋">1名主考。</span></span></p><p style="text-indent:43px"><span style=";font-family:仿宋;font-size:21px">2.</span><span style=";font-family:仿宋;font-size:21px"><span style="font-family:仿宋">面试命题。面试命题采用现场出题的方式，面试专家组提前</span><span style="font-family:仿宋">1小时现场命题。</span></span></p><p style="text-indent:43px"><span style=";font-family:仿宋;font-size:21px">3.</span><span style=";font-family:仿宋;font-size:21px">考生面试。考生提前</span><span style=";font-family:仿宋;font-size:21px">30</span><span style=";font-family:仿宋;font-size:21px">分钟</span><span style=";font-family:仿宋;font-size:21px">到达</span><span style=";font-family:仿宋;font-size:21px">候考</span><span style=";font-family:仿宋;font-size:21px">室核验身份、</span><span style=";font-family:仿宋;font-size:21px">签到</span><span style=";font-family:仿宋;font-size:21px">、提交材料，</span><span style=";font-family:仿宋;font-size:21px">按</span><span style=";font-family:仿宋;font-size:21px">指定</span><span style=";font-family:仿宋;font-size:21px">顺序逐一</span><span style=";font-family:仿宋;font-size:21px">进入面试室</span><span style=";font-family:仿宋;font-size:21px">面试</span><span style=";font-family:仿宋;font-size:21px">，</span><span style=";font-family:仿宋;font-size:21px">由考生随机</span><span style=";font-family:仿宋;font-size:21px">抽选面试题目</span><span style=";font-family:仿宋;font-size:21px">回答</span><span style=";font-family:仿宋;font-size:21px">。</span></p><p style="text-indent:43px"><span style=";font-family:仿宋;font-size:21px">4.综合</span><span style=";font-family:仿宋;font-size:21px">成绩评定。面试专家根据考生</span><span style=";font-family:仿宋;font-size:21px">现</span><span style=";font-family:仿宋;font-size:21px">场表现打分。</span></p><p style="text-indent:43px"><span style=";font-family:仿宋;font-size:21px">（</span><span style=";font-family:仿宋;font-size:21px">五</span><span style=";font-family:仿宋;font-size:21px">）</span><span style=";font-family:仿宋;font-size:21px">综合</span><span style=";font-family:仿宋;font-size:21px">成绩</span><span style=";font-family:仿宋;font-size:21px">评定规则：</span></p><p style="text-indent:43px"><span style=";font-family:仿宋;font-size:21px">1.综合</span><span style=";font-family:仿宋;font-size:21px">成绩按百分制</span><span style=";font-family:仿宋;font-size:21px">从</span><span style=";font-family:仿宋;font-size:21px"><span style="font-family:仿宋">以下方面评定</span><span style="font-family:仿宋">:</span></span></p><p style="text-indent:43px"><span style=";font-family:仿宋;font-size:21px"><span style="font-family:仿宋">（</span><span style="font-family:仿宋">1）</span></span><span style=";font-family:仿宋;font-size:21px">报考专业</span><span style=";font-family:仿宋;font-size:21px">职业适应性或职业技能</span><span style=";font-family:仿宋;font-size:21px">的掌握情况</span><span style=";font-family:仿宋;font-size:21px"><span style="font-family:仿宋">占</span><span style="font-family:仿宋">6</span></span><span style=";font-family:仿宋;font-size:21px">0%</span><span style=";font-family:仿宋;font-size:21px">。</span></p><p style="text-indent:43px"><span style=";font-family:仿宋;font-size:21px"><span style="font-family:仿宋">（</span><span style="font-family:仿宋">2）</span></span><span style=";font-family:仿宋;font-size:21px">综合素质</span><span style=";font-family:仿宋;font-size:21px">占</span><span style=";font-family:仿宋;font-size:21px">40%，包括语言表达能力、逻辑思维能力、应变能力、职业兴趣等。</span></p><p style="text-indent:43px"><span style=";font-family:仿宋;font-size:21px">2.综合</span><span style=";font-family:仿宋;font-size:21px">成绩为报考专业</span><span style=";font-family:仿宋;font-size:21px">职业适应性或职业技能</span><span style=";font-family:仿宋;font-size:21px">的掌握情况、综合素质</span><span style=";font-family:仿宋;font-size:21px">二</span><span style=";font-family:仿宋;font-size:21px">项</span><span style=";font-family:仿宋;font-size:21px">成绩</span><span style=";font-family:仿宋;font-size:21px">之和。</span><span style=";font-family:仿宋;font-size:21px">评分根据评委现场打分取其</span><span style=";font-family:仿宋;font-size:21px">平均</span><span style=";font-family:仿宋;font-size:21px">值</span><span style=";font-family:仿宋;font-size:21px">(保留2位小数点)作为考生最终成绩。</span></p><p style="text-indent:43px"><span style=";font-family:仿宋;font-size:21px">3.学校招就处</span><span style=";font-family:仿宋;font-size:21px">将</span><span style=";font-family:仿宋;font-size:21px">在规定时间内向江西省教育考试院上报综合评价合格名单。</span></p><p style="text-indent:43px"><span style=";font-family:仿宋;font-size:21px">&nbsp;</span></p><p style="text-indent:43px"><span style=";font-family:仿宋;font-size:21px">&nbsp;</span></p><p style="text-indent:43px;text-align:right"><span style=";font-family:仿宋;font-size:21px">江西软件职业技术大学</span></p><p style="text-indent:43px;text-align:right"><span style=";font-family:仿宋;font-size:21px">2024年3月25日</span></p><p style="line-height: 16px;"><img style="vertical-align: middle; margin-right: 2px;" src="/resource/js/ueditor-1.4.3.3/dialogs/attachment/fileTypeImages/icon_doc.gif"/><a style="font-size:12px; color:#0066cc;" href="/data/upload/img/20240326/1711432477933064230.docx" title="附件一.docx">附件一.docx</a></p><p><br/></p>